      <section>
         <p>The shelf life of DEF/Ad-Blue varies by storage temperature.</p>
         <p>Between 40° F and 80° F is recommended to maintain
shelf life.</p>
         <p>Above 12° F is recommended to avoid crystallization, which
starts at 11° F.</p>
         <p>Below 86° F is recommended, which cause hydrolysis to
occur, with the consequent formation of ammonia and pressure rise,
and will reduce shelf life.</p>
